item.title: Big South Bay apartment complex is bought for $200 million-plus
item.author: The Mercury News
item.description: SANTA CLARA - A big apartment complex in Santa Clara has been bought for well over $200 million in a deal that shows investors still seek to buy residential properties in the South Bay despite an uneven economy.
